headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
Those looking to get involved in Los Santos’ booming nightlife industry can purchase any Nightclub property, as well as its Upgrades and Renovations, for 40% off this week. Additionally, there is a range of vehicles discounted this week.

- Progen PR4 — 30% off
- Declasse Hotring Sabre — 40% off
- Överflöd Imorgon — 40% off
- Buckingham Alpha-Z1 — 40% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
